    SELECT t."Id", t."CategoryId", t."Description", t."DueDate", t."IsCompleted", t."Notes", t."Progress", t."Title", t."UserId"
    FROM "Tasks" AS t
    WHERE t."Id" = @__id_0
    LIMIT 1
) AS t1
LEFT JOIN "TaskTags" AS t0 ON t1."Id" = t0."TaskId"
ORDER BY t1."Id", t0."TaskId"
